lead_paragraph: Players involved in a mixed doubles match at the Australian Open said Monday they were interviewed by the Tennis Integrity Unit after a newspaper reported it had attracted suspicious betting patterns.

headline.print_headline: Tennis Officials Interview Players Over Mixed Doubles Match
